geant4 main program and configuration file
- sim_atomx.cc # will be compiled to sim_atomx.exe at compilation time
- configure.mac # main configuration file for running lilak-geant4-nptool. read the comments inside

nptool input files
- #PhysicsListOption.txt # This is read from PhysicsList class
- nptool_34Ar_alpha_p.reaction # or any other default reaction files can be used
- nptool_cs_flat.txt # Cross section file. This is coupleed with reaction file
- #project.config # this doesn't have to contain anything

Geant4 macros:
- geant4_nptool_vis.mac
- geant4_vis.mac
